reviews.review_text: Underated Show. The slightly better sounding of the two sources. Sounds good, not great(Not bad for a Civic Center pull). The show itself is very well played. The long first set is nice, with hot versions of Shakedown and Music.  Set two is solid throughout, with a nice He's Gone>Truckin>Spoonful>Space Jam. The Watchtower>Dew, is quite hot also. The Space jam is included with the Drums on this version.
